{"id":1768,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":481,"title":"Conversation 241","subtitle":"Projector Offer for Meeting","level":"B1","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-241.1768/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-241-2024-10-29-23-05-48/0-conversation-241.mp3","transcript":"Hey, I heard you're setting up a small meeting area in your office.\nDo you need an extra projector?\nActually, that would be great!\nWe were just planning on ordering one.\nIs it from your department?\nYeah, we just upgraded, so we don't need this one anymore.\nIt's in good shape, and I think it could be useful for your setup.\nThat sounds perfect.\nDo you mind if I check it out later?\nSure thing!\nIt's still set up in our conference room.\nI'll be around until 4 pm,\nso feel free to pop in and test it out.\nThanks, I'll swing by later and give it a try!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:04:07","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Hey, I heard you're setting up a small meeting area in your office.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-241-2024-10-29-23-05-48/1.mp3","time_start":0.0,"time_end":3.8},{"position":2,"content":"Do you need an extra projector?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-241-2024-10-29-23-05-48/2.mp3","time_start":3.8,"time_end":5.67},{"position":3,"content":"Actually, that would be great!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-241-2024-10-29-23-05-48/3.mp3","time_start":5.67,"time_end":7.4},{"position":4,"content":"We were just planning on ordering one.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-241-2024-10-29-23-05-48/4.mp3","time_start":7.4,"time_end":9.17},{"position":5,"content":"Is it from your department?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-241-2024-10-29-23-05-48/5.mp3","time_start":9.17